\fIwcstombs\fP() shall return (\fBsize_t\fP)-1. Otherwise, \fIwcstombs\fP()
shall return tha number of bytes stored up in the
characta array, not includin any terminatin null byte. Da array
shall not be null-terminated if tha value returned is
\fIn\fP.
